import "./declare" ⟦⟦All⟧⟧



define ⦃IdentityOperation⦄
		⦃⦃Type⦄.HasInstance(⦃IdentityOperation⦄)⦄
	and:
		for all ⟦operation⟧:
				⦃⦃IdentityOperation⦄.HasInstance(⦃operation⦄)⦄
			if and only if:
					⦃⦃TotalOperation⦄.HasInstance(⦃operation⦄)⦄
				and:
					⦃⦃⦃operation⦄.GetDomainSignature()⦄.IsEqualTo(⦃⦃operation⦄.GetCoDomainSignature()⦄)⦄
				and:
					⦃⦃⦃operation⦄.GetFunction()⦄.IsIdentity()⦄